---
title: Double Spiced Chicken & Zesty Roast Veggie Toss with Hollandaise & Almonds
description: There’s something special about a root vegetable, we can’t get enough of them! Therefore, this dish is chocked full of those yummy colourful veggies. Gently spiced chicken is cooked to juicy tender perfection and a drizzle of hollandaise adds extra flavour.

*We’ve replaced the walnuts in this recipe with slivered almonds due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as
delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66062bf5fc49d1f9cc477626-09140f4a.jpeg
